      <section class="region region-sidebar-second column sidebar">
       <div class="block block-views first odd module clearfix" id="block-views-homepage-mini-features-block">
        <div class="block-content">
         <div class="view view-homepage-mini-features view-id-homepage_mini_features view-display-id-block view-dom-id-d616a883e81b0224eeb51fe8cadc4ed1">
          <div class="view-content">
           <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
            <article class="node-176 node node-homepage-mini-feature view-mode-full clearfix">
             <span>
              <img alt="" src="http://biologicalsciences.uchicago.edu/sites/biologicalsciences.uchicago.edu/files/styles/columnwidth-wider/public/uploads/images/Polonsky%2020150325_Medicine_3689b.jpg?itok=znOkunEm"/>
             </span>
             <h2>
              About the Dean
             </h2>
             <p>
              Kenneth S. Polonsky, MD, has served as Dean of the Biological Sciences Division and the Pritzker School of Medicine and EVP for Medical Affairs of the University of Chicago since October 2010. Â He is the Richard T. Crane Distinguished Service Professor and a prominent diabetes researcher, physician and educator.
             </p>
             <p>
              Read the
              <a href="/blog">
               Dean's Corner
              </a>
              blog.
             </p>
            </article>
